      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.6EJMD8EZbjuSnJPs]{Farshot}</p>\n<p>You gain the increased critical hit damage and increased critical effect save DC of your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.ImjaNm30BZQWVhGk]{patient precision} ability whenever you perform an aimed shot. If you use patient precision to aim as a full action (or as a standard action with instant aim), the next aimed shot you attempt before the end of your next turn scores a critical hit dealing double damage on a natural die result of 18 or 19, and it scores a critical hit dealing the full triple damage on a natural die result of 20.</p>"
